# 🧱 STATE REDUCER DESIGN (CORE ENGINE)

This is your central mutation engine:

```js id="reducer1"
function applyEffect(state, effect) {

  switch(effect.type) {

    case "grantItem":
      state.inventory[effect.payload.itemId] =
        (state.inventory[effect.payload.itemId] || 0)
        + effect.payload.amount;
      break;

    case "setFlag":
      state.flags[effect.payload.flagId] =
        effect.payload.value;
      break;

    case "incrementStat":
      state.stats[effect.payload.statId] =
        (state.stats[effect.payload.statId] || 0)
        + effect.payload.value;
      break;

    case "grantReward":
      state.rewards[effect.payload.rewardId] = {
        claimed: true,
        timestamp: Date.now()
      };
      break;
  }

  return state;
}
```

